    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Functional \u2014 A Fair-Condition Car at an Honest Price! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's got some miles and life on it, and we're upfront about that! You'll notice visible wear on the interior and exterior, and it may have a few minor mechanical quirks worth addressing, but it runs and gets you where you need to go. It's a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer who doesn't mind a little character and is comfortable with some upcoming maintenance. Priced fairly to reflect its true condition \u2014 no surprises here, just a straightforward deal! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a clear and honest picture before you consider making a purchase. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 you can expect several scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading consistent with a car that has seen regular use over the years. The interior is functional but worn; upholstery shows signs of use, and some trim pieces may show age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price point, with eyes open to the car's current state.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a parts vehicle? This car could be just the opportunity you've been waiting for! We'll be straight with you \u2014 this one is in poor condition, showing significant wear both inside and out, and will require mechanical attention to get it running reliably. It's priced accordingly to reflect its current state, making it a solid pick for a handy buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for an affordable fix-up challenge. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Fixer \u2014 Priced to Reflect Its Condition! \u2014 Looking for an affordable project car or a no-frills runner on a tight budget? This vehicle is honestly priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it has seen better days and will need some work. Mechanically, it has issues that should be addressed, and the overall wear is noticeable inside and out. That said, it's a real opportunity for a handy buyer or someone who just needs basic transportation and is comfortable with its limitations. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects exactly that!",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in good condition, and prospective buyers can expect a reliable, well-maintained option that shows normal signs of use but remains in solid overall shape. The exterior presents well with only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with regular driving \u2014 think small surface scratches or light paint wear \u2014 but no major dents, rust, or structural concerns. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing moderate wear on high-contact areas such as the driver's seat and door panels, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or appearance. Mechanically, the vehicle runs reliably; routine maintenance has been kept up, and there are no known major mechanical issues. All primary systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and HVAC \u2014 are in working order. This is a solid everyday driver that has been cared for and offers good value for a buyer seeking dependable transportation without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we stand behind that description completely. The exterior paint is rich, deep, and glossy \u2014 completely free of scratches, dents, chips, or any blemishes whatsoever. The body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim pieces are intact and pristine. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor: no stains, no wear on the seats or carpeting, no cracked or faded surfaces anywhere. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, and the mechanical systems are in excellent working order. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally cared for \u2014 a true turn-key, worry-free ownership experience from day one.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    }
